# Environment variables — NEVER commit. Real secrets belong in AWS Secrets
# Manager / SSM (runtime) and GitHub Secrets (CI auth). Only the no-secrets
# template `.env.example` is allowed in git.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

/src/generated/prisma

